text: Alta Kotze (born 4 December 1971) is an international cricketer who made 18 One Day International appearances for South Africa national women's cricket team between 1997 and 1999. == References == == External links== * * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Cricketers from Johannesburg Category:South African women cricketers Category:South Africa women One Day International cricketers
